title: Alibaba : mobile user MAU Q4 2016-Q4 2019
yAxis: Active Alibaba mobile users in millions
summary: This statistic shows the Active millions of mobile in the consumer price index , respectively the user Active Alibaba for goods and services in the Alibaba .
The data represents mobile city averages .
In economics , the Active Alibaba is a measure of Active , the Alibaba of increasing a price index ( in the below case : consumer price index ) .
gold: This statistic gives information on the consolidated number of monthly active mobile users ( MAU ) across Alibaba 's online shopping properties from the fourth quarter of 2016 to the fourth quarter of 2019 . As of the last quarter of 2019 , Alibaba 's Chinese e-commerce properties had been accessed by around 824 million mobile MAU .
